==English==

===Etymology===
After ''[[Narcissus]]'', the fictional Greek hero who became obsessed with his own reflection.

===Pronunciation===
*/{{IPAchar|ˈnɑːsəˌsɪzm}}/

===Noun===
'''narcissism'''

# [[egoism|Egoism]]; [[egocentrism]].
# Love of oneself.
# Sexual [[desire]] for one's own body.

